data.description: Introducing your dream home!  Welcome to the perfect blend of comfort and convenience in this charming end-unit with a garage & fenced backyard. Step into your home sweet home through the foyer entrance, leading to a spacious family room ideal for gatherings and cozy evenings.  Whip up some culinary delights in the well-appointed kitchen with a classic eat-in kitchen area, perfect for family dinners.  Upstairs, discover a serene oasis with 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths, to include an owners retreat featuring a delightful sitting area, your personal haven of relaxation. This unit happens to be the only unit for sale in the entire subdivision with a fenced backyard, perfect for pet lovers, or private outdoor BBQs.  This unit also offers a front porch area where you can enjoy your morning cup of coffee in a comfy rocking.  There's a bonus... the seller is leaving the washer and dryer for your convenience, making moving a breeze.  This townhome is conveniently located only 13 minutes from Hartsfield Airport and 18 minutes from downtown Atlanta, a short drive to catch a show at the Fox Theater or have dinner in the city.  The unit has easy access to I75, and public transportation is just steps away.  There are no rental restrictions, so you can easily purchase this unit and rent it out to add to your rental portfolio.  Don't miss this exclusive opportunity to call this end unit townhome yours.  Schedule a showing before it's gone tomorrow.
